T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開窗就無左啦隻蚊</blockquote><br />\n得啦得啦"},{"pid":"753aabdbd74b092393a52f52dad5e228328189c5","tid":447034,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>若果架車係密閉空間 姐係車入面冇任何氣體 隻蚊再向前飛既話 相對地面黎講 佢係飛得快過架車<br />\n因為密閉空間內 隻蚊當做車既其中一部分 有車既速率慣性</blockquote><br />\nfail, 冇氣體隻蚊根本飛唔到</blockquote><br />\n打少左 係冇任何氣體流動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果架車冇加速/減速就係姐<br />\n問題係點解架車加/減緊速個時，你唔會見隻蚊好似人咁側埋一邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7744fb04ad6a7a6fe2ba7842e2bdf3a391fd4f","tid":447034,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗下係火車入面放個氫氣球<br />\n火車加速時個氣球係向前定向後<br />\n你就會知答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇人試下答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前既正評<br />\n後既負評<br />\n答得岩應該就會明其實樓主個問題唔太關慣性事</blockquote><br />\n開估先<br />\n其實個波會向前<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y8mzDvpKzfY&amp;t=171s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy8mzDvpKzfY%26t%3D171s&d=uBVAaNA4o%2FoePBNApAJECNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=999b7073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y8mzDvpKzfY&amp;t=171s</a>"},{"pid":"2239c25df9b6b92f3e43194a171d8478e187a3fa","tid":447034,"uid":35625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"你原地自轉，地球亦都自轉。咁你自轉咪快過地球"},{"pid":"efa6d0563a2861042d48bc80ef7d6eed70dd8f68","tid":447034,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:17:28.000Z","msg":"呢條問題同以下兩個問題其實並稱廿一世紀三大on9仔專屬既難題。<br />\n<br />\n一。 推一條長一光秒既棍 = 超光速？<br />\n<br />\n二。 拎住電筒向前行。電筒既光 = 光速+你既行速 = 超光速"},{"pid":"a24d2af63b6840012832a67facbe9d084a790671","tid":447034,"uid":5190,"li