915589a666899ae5382aab0b67ad","tid":447034,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會有人認真討論..😌"},{"pid":"3b10afcd7d9b8c4df191d98b710b6024256fcb65","tid":447034,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"你喺狗鐵入邊打飛機射牆角， 分分鐘射穿牆"},{"pid":"2065c8fbaa847e98906420bbaf0c9ef738ade13f","tid":447034,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會有人認真討論..😌</blockquote><br />\n試過坐巴士見到有隻蚊無論架巴士轉左轉右向前向後都仲係你面前飛未?<br />\n<br />\n當你坐最前面, 諗住架巴士開車隻蚊就會飛去後面個時<br />\n但事實係隻蚊仲係你面前/隔離飛緊, 你就知呢個問題一d都唔簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9494909e2e9d4d18e589ce9c76e92dd5ffcede","tid":447034,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"佢識雷切"}]}